  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Start your day with a buffet breakfast with pastries, cakes, fresh bread, jams, cold cuts, cheeses, cooked options, teas and coffees. </p>
<p>The restaurants a popular spot, serving lunch and evening meals. The food is delicious home cooked fare. You can dine a la carte or choose to stay half board for a supplement. The food is all freshly made to order and you'll be served a f<span>our course meal that you can choose from the menu the evening before. In nice weather you can dine in the garden. </span></p>
<p>During the summer season the hotel have themed events and and food and wine evenings in their gardens. Its a nice way to try the food and wine from local producers. </p>
<p>There's a small bar area with a good selection of wines and spirits. It's a nice area to relax with a post dinner drinks. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
