  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Beach &amp; Gardens</strong></span></p>
<p><span>Lido di Camaiore beach stretches for four kilometers between Viareggio, Marina di Pietrasanta and Forte dei Marmi. </span>The hotel offer discounted rates for hiring sun loungers at the beach down the road (payable locally).</p>
<p>The spacious hotel gardens are equipped with sun loungers, tables and chairs, providing a nice space to relax outside. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Activities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free use of hotel bikes for pleasant rides along the seafront</li>
<li>Versilia Golf Club, 18-hole course (payable locally)</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi aprrox. €5 per week (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
