  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The family run Hotel Fortunella is the perfect base for making the most of <a data-udi="umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58d85ec0faa548b2ab580143fdc9b722}" title="Tuscany &amp; Umbria">Tuscany's</a> sun and sea, just minutes from the beach. It's perfectly located for exploring further afield too, with great transport links to Tuscan towns and cities like Lucca, Florence and Pisa. </p>]]></listingDescription>
